Comment: 0,0:01:19.01,0:01:25.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}崩れて終わる世界
Comment: 0,0:01:25.44,0:01:34.40,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}無慈悲に告げる
Comment: 0,0:01:35.03,0:01:40.99,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}君は  一人
Comment: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:47.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}何を  聞いてた
Comment: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:53.76,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}僕は  遠い
Comment: 0,0:01:54.17,0:02:00.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}夢を  見てた
Comment: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:02.18,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}何を選び取る
Comment: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:03.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}何を諦める
Comment: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:05.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}決めようとしてる
Comment: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:07.02,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}僕は何様だ
Comment: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:08.60,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}何を選ぶかは
Comment: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:10.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}もう決まっている
Comment: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:11.81,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}間違いは無いか
Comment: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:13.15,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}神に問いかける
Comment: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:16.15,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}一人きりじゃなかった
Comment: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:18.82,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}ずっとそばにいたんだ
Comment: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:25.79,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}この手を伸ばす
Comment: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:28.92,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}怖いものなんかない
Comment: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:32.63,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}たとえ化け物になろうとも
Comment: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:40.64,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord2\be6\blur4}成し遂げる
Comment: 0,0:01:19.01,0:01:25.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}崩壞的終焉之世
Comment: 0,0:01:25.44,0:01:34.40,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}無情告知
Comment: 0,0:01:34.94,0:01:41.24,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}你默默一人
Comment: 0,0:01:41.45,0:01:47.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}在聆聽什麼
Comment: 0,0:01:47.83,0:01:53.76,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}而我恍惚
Comment: 0,0:01:54.17,0:02:00.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}如在遠夢中彷徨
Comment: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:02.18,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}選擇什麼
Comment: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:03.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}放棄什麼
Comment: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:05.39,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}我有何權力
Comment: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:07.02,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}做這些決定
Comment: 0,0:02:07.06,0:02:08.60,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}如何選擇
Comment: 0,0:02:08.65,0:02:10.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}已經確定
Comment: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:11.81,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}有否錯誤
Comment: 0,0:02:11.81,0:02:13.15,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}向神詢問
Comment: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:16.15,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}你不是一個人
Comment: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:18.82,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}一直在你身邊
Comment: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:25.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}將這雙手伸出
Comment: 0,0:02:26.00,0:02:28.92,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}無所畏懼
Comment: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:32.63,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}就算是化身怪物
Comment: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:40.64,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,300)\bord\be6\blur4}定將完成夙願
